column2: justin bieber help baby mariahs dream come true
column5: Mariah suffers from a rare brain disorder called schizencephaly caused by a utero stroke she will wheelchair bound she doesn't speak she suffers from seizures daily and has lost part of her eyesight Mariah has many challenges everyday she fights for her life! But one person can bring out so much joy is JB! Please sign and share and help this lil girl! Thanks to learn about about schizencephaly and to help other children please visit noahscart.org thank u.
